-news.co.uk/article.cfm?id=113993&headline=Ceredigion%E2%80%99s+MP+reacts+to+surprise+news+of+snap+General+Election&sectionIs=news&searchyear=2017|title=Ceredigion's MP reacts to surprise news of snap General Election|publisher=}}</ref>\n  |votes      = 11,519\n  |percentage = 29.0\n  |change     = -6.9\n}}\n{{Election box candidate with party link|\n  |party      = Labour Party (UK)\n  |candidate  = Dinah Mulholland<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.morningstaronline.co.uk/t2cce00-dinah-mulholland|title=Dinah Mulholland|first=People's Printing Press|last=Society|publisher=}}{{Dead link|date=November 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>\n  |votes      = 8,017\n  |percentage = 20.2\n  |change     = +10.5\n}}\n{{Election box candidate with party link|\n  |party      = Conservative Party (UK)\n  |candidate  = [[Ruth Edwards|Ruth Davis]]\n  |votes      = 7,307\n  |percentage = 18.4\n  |change     = +7.4\n}}\n{{Election box candidate with party link|\n  |party      = UK Independence Party\n  |candidate  = Tom Harrison\n  |votes      = 602\n  |percentage = 1.5\n  |change     = -8.7\n}}\n{{Election box candidate with party link|\n  |party      = Green Party of England and Wales\n  |candidate  = Grenville Ham\n  |votes      = 542\n  |percentage = 1.4\n  |change     = -4.2\n}}\n{{Election box candidate with party link|\n  |party      = Official Monster Raving Loony Party\n  |candidate  = Sir Dudley the Crazed<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.loonyparty.com/0807/5939/general-election-candiadtes/| title=Loony Party Candidates| accessdate=7 May 2017}}</ref>\n  |votes      = 157\n  |percentage = 0.4\t\n  |change     = ''N/A''\n}}\n{{Election box rejected\n  |votes      = 52\n  |percentage = \n  |change     = \n}}\n{{Election box majority|\n  |votes      = 104\t\n  |percentage = 0.2\n  |change     = ''N/A''\n}}\n{{Election box turnout|\n  |votes      = 39,767\n  |percentage = 75.2\n  |change     = +6.2\n}}\n{{Election box registered electors|\n  |reg. electors = 52